10. Movie-Genre:epic is on the left or right of Game:mah-jongg
11. Game:canastas is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:scientific
12. Movie-Genre:junemaster == House:modern
13. Sport:tennis == Movie-Genre:spy
14. Sport:rugby is on the left or right of Birthday:june
15. Movie-Genre:epic is on the left or right of House:tower

